License: Commercial
Vendor: Temerity Software, Inc
Group: Applications/Productivity
BuildRoot: @RPM_ROOT@/BUILD

%description
Pipeline consists of a suite of programs which use a high-level node based representation of 
the production process to peform a wide range of visualization, automation and administrative
services.

The core features of Pipeline include: 
  + Graphical tools to visualize and control the production process.
  + Advanced revision control of production data files, processes and dependencies.
  + Modeling of arbitrarily complex production pipeline's.
  + Automatic generation of jobs needed to complete a production process.
  + Execution of jobs both locally and by a distributed execution queue.
  + Automation of data archiving and restoration.
  + Command-line based scripting of all functionality.
  + Rich Java based plugin API allowing almost unlimited customization and extension.

